title: Sailing at the 2004 Summer Olympics – Star
text: The Men's <a href="Star%20%28sailboat%29">Star</a> was a sailing event on the <a href="Sailing%20at%20the%202004%20Summer%20Olympics">Sailing at the 2004 Summer Olympics</a> program in <a href="Agios%20Kosmas%20Olympic%20Sailing%20Centre">Agios Kosmas Olympic Sailing Centre</a>. Eleven races were scheduled and completed with one discard. 34 sailors, on 17 boats, from 17 nation competed.
